---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Seluruh Layanan Kami | LUMOVELO" description="Layanan lengkap pembuatan website berkinerja tinggi, optimasi SEO organik, dan solusi otomatisasi AI & WhatsApp untuk bisnis Anda.">
  
  <!-- Header Nav (Sticky) -->
  <header class="w-full z-50 border-b border-slate-200 bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-md sticky top-0">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 h-20 flex items-center justify-between">
      <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3 group">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl border-2 border-slate-900 bg-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center shadow-[3px_3px_0px_#0f172a] group-hover:translate-x-0.5 group-hover:translate-y-0.5 group-hover:shadow-[1px_1px_0px_#0f172a] transition-all duration-200">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <polyline points="13 17 18 12 13 7"></polyline>
            <polyline points="6 17 11 12 6 7"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <span class="font-display font-black text-xl tracking-widest text-slate-900 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">LUMOVELO</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg border-2 border-slate-200 hover:border-slate-400 bg-white text-slate-700 hover:text-slate-900 text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider transition-all select-none">
        Kembali Ke Beranda
      </a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="relative z-10 bg-white">
    <!-- Hero Header -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-slate-50 border-b border-slate-200 relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(rgba(37,99,235,0.015)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:1.5rem_1.5rem] pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
        <h1 class="font-mono font-bold text-xs tracking-widest text-blue-600 uppercase">/ LAYANAN LENGKAP</h1>
        <h2 class="font-display font-black text-4xl sm:text-6xl text-slate-900 tracking-tight leading-[1.0] uppercase mt-3">
          Eksplorasi Solusi Kami.<br/>
          <span class="text-stroke-neon">Sesuai Kebutuhan Bisnis Anda.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-slate-500 mt-6 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed font-semibold max-w-2xl">
          Dari pembuatan website performa tinggi hingga integrasi otomatisasi WhatsApp dan AI, kami siap membantu bisnis Anda beroperasi secara maksimal.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 1: JASA PEMBUATAN WEBSITE -->
    <section class="py-20 border-b border-slate-200">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="mb-12">
          <span class="font-mono font-bold text-xs tracking-widest text-blue-600 uppercase">/ LAYANAN UTAMA</span>
          <h3 class="font-display font-black text-3xl text-slate-900 uppercase mt-2">Jasa Pembuatan Website</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs sm:text-sm mt-2 font-semibold">Tersedia dalam 4 pilihan paket investasi sekali bayar sesuai skala kebutuhan bisnis Anda.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
          <!-- Paket 1 -->
          <div class="service-card border-2 border-blue-600 bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-3xl relative shadow-[4px_4px_0px_#2563eb] hover:shadow-[6px_6px_0px_#1d4ed8] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[460px]">
            <div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-6">
                <span class="text-[9px] font-mono text-slate-500 bg-white border border-slate-200 px-2 py-0.5 rounded font-bold">PAKET_01</span>
                <span class="text-[9px] font-black text-blue-600 uppercase">PROFIL BISNIS</span>
              </div>
              <h4 class="font-display font-black text-lg text-slate-900 uppercase leading-snug">Landing Page / Company Profile</h4>
              <div class="my-4">
                <div class="text-[9px] font-mono text-slate-450 font-bold uppercase">Sekali Bayar</div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-display font-black text-blue-600 mt-0.5">Rp 1.500.000</div>
              </div>
              <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-xs text-slate-600 font-semibold mb-6">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-blue-600 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span>Domain (.com/.id) & Hosting 1 tahun</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-blue-600 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span>1 Halaman penjualan konversi tinggi</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-blue-600 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span>Desain kustom responsif & modern</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-blue-600 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span>Integrasi tombol WhatsApp direct</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-blue-600 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span>Batas Revisi: 3 kali</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <a href="/#konsultasi" class="w-full inline-flex items-center justify-center py-3 rounded-xl border-2 border-blue-600 bg-white hover:bg-slate-50 text-blue-600 font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-wider transition-all duration-200 shadow-[3px_3px_0px_#2563eb] active:translate-y-0.5 active:shadow-[1px_1px_0px_#2563eb] cursor-pointer">Pilih Paket</a>
          </div>

          <!-- Paket 2 -->
          <div class="service-card border-2 border-slate-900 bg-white p-6 rounded-3xl relative shadow-[5px_5px_0px_#2563eb] hover:shadow-[7px_7px_0px_#1d4ed8] hover:-translate-y-1.5 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[480px] z-10">
            <div class="absolute top-0 right-6 -translate-y-1/2 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full border-2 border-slate-900 bg-amber-400 text-[8px] font-mono font-black text-slate-900 uppercase tracking-widest shadow-[1px_1px_0px_#0f172a]">Populer</div>
            <div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-6">
                <span class="text-[9px] font-mono text-white bg-slate-900 border border-slate-900 px-2 py-0.5 rounded font-bold">PAKET_02</span>
                <span class="text-[9px] font-black text-blue-600 uppercase">TOKO ONLINE</span>
              </div>
              <h4 class="font-display font-black text-lg text-slate-900 uppercase leading-snug">E-Commerce / Toko Online</h4>
              <div class="my-4">
                <div class="text-[9px] font-mono text-slate-450 font-bold uppercase">Sekali Bayar</div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-display font-black text-blue-600 mt-0.5">Rp 3.000.000</div>
              </div>
              <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-xs text-slate-600 font-semibold mb-6">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-blue-600 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span>Domain (.com/.id) & Hosting 1 tahun</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-blue-600 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span>Katalog & keranjang belanja (up to 50 produk)</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-blue-600 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span>Form pemesanan otomatis ke WhatsApp</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-blue-600 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span>Dashboard Admin HP (kelola produk & stok)</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-blue-600 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span>Batas Revisi: 5 kali</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <a href="/#konsultasi" class="w-full inline-flex items-center justify-center py-3 rounded-xl border-2 border-blue-600 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-wider transition-all duration-200 shadow-[3px_3px_0px_#0f172a] active:translate-y-0.5 active:shadow-[1px_1px_0px_#0f172a] cursor-pointer">Pilih Paket</a>
          </div>

          <!-- Paket 3 -->
          <div class="service-card border-2 border-blue-600 bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-3xl relative shadow-[4px_4px_0px_#2563eb] hover:shadow-[6px_6px_0px_#1d4ed8] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[460px]">
            <div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-6">
                <span class="text-[9px] font-mono text-slate-500 bg-white border border-slate-200 px-2 py-0.5 rounded font-bold">PAKET_03</span>
                <span class="text-[9px] font-black text-blue-600 uppercase">WEB PORTAL</span>
              </div>
              <h4 class="font-display font-black text-lg text-slate-900 uppercase leading-snug">Web Kustom / Aplikasi Portal</h4>
              <div class="my-4">
                <div class="text-[9px] font-mono text-slate-450 font-bold uppercase">Sekali Bayar</div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-display font-black text-slate-900 mt-0.5">Rp 5.000.000</div>
              </div>
              <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-xs text-slate-600 font-semibold mb-6">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-blue-600 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span>Sistem login & registrasi keanggotaan user</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-blue-600 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span>Integrasi pembayaran otomatis (Midtrans/Xendit)</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-blue-600 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span>Sistem cek tarif & pelacakan ongkir otomatis</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-blue-600 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span>Jaminan performa tinggi & data aman</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-blue-600 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span>Batas Revisi: 7 kali</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <a href="/#konsultasi" class="w-full inline-flex items-center justify-center py-3 rounded-xl border-2 border-blue-600 bg-white hover:bg-slate-50 text-blue-600 font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-wider transition-all duration-200 shadow-[3px_3px_0px_#2563eb] active:translate-y-0.5 active:shadow-[1px_1px_0px_#2563eb] cursor-pointer">Pilih Paket</a>
          </div>

          <!-- Paket 4 -->
          <div class="service-card border-2 border-blue-600 bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-3xl relative shadow-[4px_4px_0px_#2563eb] hover:shadow-[6px_6px_0px_#1d4ed8] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[460px]">
            <div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-6">
                <span class="text-[9px] font-mono text-slate-500 bg-white border border-slate-200 px-2 py-0.5 rounded font-bold">PAKET_04</span>
                <span class="text-[9px] font-black text-blue-600 uppercase">CUSTOM</span>
              </div>
              <h4 class="font-display font-black text-lg text-slate-900 uppercase leading-snug">Sistem Khusus / Enterprise</h4>
              <div class="my-4">
                <div class="text-[9px] font-mono text-slate-450 font-bold uppercase">Investasi Mulai Dari</div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-display font-black text-slate-900 mt-0.5">Hubungi Kami</div>
              </div>
              <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-xs text-slate-600 font-semibold mb-6">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-blue-600 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span>Arsitektur sistem kompleks & integrasi API khusus</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-blue-600 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span>Visualisasi dasbor analitik bisnis real-time</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-blue-600 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span>Otomatisasi sistem manajemen CRM internal</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-blue-600 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span>Jaminan keamanan & enkripsi data tingkat tinggi</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-blue-600 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span>Revisi tanpa batas selama masa pengembangan</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <a href="/#konsultasi" class="w-full inline-flex items-center justify-center py-3 rounded-xl border-2 border-blue-600 bg-white hover:bg-slate-50 text-blue-600 font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-wider transition-all duration-200 shadow-[3px_3px_0px_#2563eb] active:translate-y-0.5 active:shadow-[1px_1px_0px_#2563eb] cursor-pointer">Hubungi Kami</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 2: JASA SEO -->
    <section class="py-20 border-b border-slate-200 bg-slate-50/50">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="border-2 border-blue-600 bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-[5px_5px_0px_#2563eb] reveal-on-scroll">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between gap-6 mb-8 pb-6 border-b border-slate-100">
            <div>
              <span class="font-mono font-bold text-xs tracking-widest text-blue-600 uppercase">/ OPTIMISASI PENCARIAN</span>
              <h3 class="font-display font-black text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-slate-900 uppercase mt-2">Jasa SEO (Search Engine Optimization)</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="text-left md:text-right shrink-0">
              <div class="text-[9px] font-mono text-slate-400 font-bold uppercase">Investasi Layanan</div>
              <div class="text-xl font-display font-black text-blue-600">Rp 1.000.000 - Custom</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-semibold mb-8">
            Dapatkan trafik kunjungan organik berkelanjutan dari hasil pencarian Google. Kami mengoptimasi struktur teknis, konten, dan kecepatan muat situs Anda agar mendominasi peringkat kata kunci lokal maupun nasional.
          </p>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-8">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3.5"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div class="space-y-1">
                <h5 class="text-xs font-display font-black text-slate-900 uppercase">Riset Kata Kunci Bisnis</h5>
                <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 font-medium">Mencari frasa yang paling sering diketik calon pembeli Anda.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3.5"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div class="space-y-1">
                <h5 class="text-xs font-display font-black text-slate-900 uppercase">Optimasi Halaman (On-Page)</h5>
                <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 font-medium">Mengatur meta tags, headings, dan struktur artikel.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3.5"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div class="space-y-1">
                <h5 class="text-xs font-display font-black text-slate-900 uppercase">SEO Teknis & Kecepatan</h5>
                <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 font-medium">Mempercepat loading web agar disukai algoritma Google.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3.5"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div class="space-y-1">
                <h5 class="text-xs font-display font-black text-slate-900 uppercase">Integrasi Alat Pelacak</h5>
                <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 font-medium">Menyinkronkan Google Search Console & Analytics.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6 pt-6 border-t border-slate-100">
            <span class="text-[9px] font-mono text-slate-400 font-bold">LUMOVELO // SEO_SUITE_SYSTEM</span>
            <a 
              href="/#konsultasi" 
              class="w-full sm:w-auto inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3.5 rounded-xl border-2 border-blue-600 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-widest transition-all duration-200 shadow-[3px_3px_0px_#0f172a] active:translate-y-0.5 active:shadow-[1px_1px_0px_#0f172a] cursor-pointer"
            >
              Hubungi Kami
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 3: JASA AI & OTOMATISASI -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="border-2 border-blue-600 bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-[5px_5px_0px_#2563eb] reveal-on-scroll">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between gap-6 mb-8 pb-6 border-b border-slate-100">
            <div>
              <span class="font-mono font-bold text-xs tracking-widest text-blue-600 uppercase">/ OTOMATISASI PINTAR</span>
              <h3 class="font-display font-black text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-slate-900 uppercase mt-2">AI & Otomatisasi Bisnis</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="text-left md:text-right shrink-0">
              <div class="text-[9px] font-mono text-slate-440 font-bold uppercase">Investasi Layanan</div>
              <div class="text-xl font-display font-black text-blue-600">Rp 2.000.000 - Custom</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-semibold mb-8">
            Minimalkan beban kerja operasional harian yang repetitif. Kami membangun integrasi sistem WhatsApp auto-responder, sinkronisasi otomatis formulir prospek langsung ke lembar kerja admin, serta chatbot asisten AI interaktif.
          </p>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8">
            <div class="flex flex-col justify-between p-5 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl min-h-[140px]">
              <h5 class="text-xs font-display font-black text-slate-900 uppercase">WhatsApp Responder</h5>
              <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 font-semibold leading-relaxed mt-2">Kirim pesan balasan otomatis seketika saat form di website disubmit pembeli.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col justify-between p-5 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl min-h-[140px]">
              <h5 class="text-xs font-display font-black text-slate-900 uppercase">Google Sheet Sync</h5>
              <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 font-semibold leading-relaxed mt-2">Data pembeli otomatis tercatat di Google Sheets tanpa perlu salin-tempel manual.</p>
            </div>
